Film Producer, Kenneth Nkosi allegedly assaulted a woman in Newtown on Friday. According to a tweet circulating on social media, Kenneth was at BlackAnt Lounge in Newtwon when the ordeal occurred. The actor wanted the woman's attention, and when she was not interested, Kenneth allegedly assaulted her, followed her to the restrooms and continued to violate her. There is a video that shows intoxicated Kenneth refusing to give back the lady her phone, a phone that he allegedly took while he was beating her up and he is heard saying he does not want to. A case has been opened against Kenneth. The tweet has gotten people speaking out on Kenneth’s "usual" behaviour.     